\sum_{k=0}^n \binom{n}{k} k^2 = n(n+1) 2^{n-2}
k\ge 2,
k^2\binom nk=\{k(k-1)+k\}\binom nk
=k(k-1)n(n-1)\frac{(n-2)!}{(k-2)!k(k-1)\{(n-2)-(k-2)\}!}+kn\frac{(n-1)!}{(k-1)! k \{(n-1)-(k-1)\}}
=n(n-1)\binom{n-2}{k-2}+n\binom{n-1}{k-1}
\sum_{0\le k\le n}k^2\binom nk
=n(n-1)\sum_{2\le k\le n}\binom{n-2}{k-2}+n\sum_{1\le k\le n}\binom{n-1}{k-1}
=n(n-1)(1+1)^{n-2}+n(1+1)^{n-1}
